        {
            "id": 6436331,
            "title": "盤中速報 - 乙盛-KY(5243)大漲7.21%，報107元",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>乙盛-KY(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:5243:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/5243\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">5243-TW</a>)29日11:44股價上漲7.2元，報107.0元，漲幅7.21%，成交6,901張。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>乙盛-KY(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:5243:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/5243\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">5243-TW</a>)所屬產業為光電業，主要業務為模具、塑膠及五金製品之設計、研發、生產及銷售。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>近5日股價下跌16.13%，集中市場<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/TWS/TSE01\">加權指數</a>上漲5.1%，短期股價無明顯表現。</p></section><section><p><em>近5日籌碼</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>三大法人合計買賣超：-7,261 張</li> <li>外資買賣超：-6,165 張</li> <li>投信買賣超：-1 張</li> <li>自營商買賣超：-1,095 張</li> <li>融資增減：-844 張</li> <li>融券增減：-35 張</li> </ul></section></main>",
